s\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Boerne, Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boerne,_Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boerne,_Texas\"}, {\"begin\": 309, \"end\": 322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boerne,_Texas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Boerne, Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boerne,_Texas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boerne,_Texas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interview withHoda\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 261}, {\"ngram\": \"Retton's home\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 305}, {\"ngram\": \"the 55-year-old icon\", \"from\": 324, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"every day\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 378}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 386}, {\"ngram\": \"so many unanswered questions\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 439}, {\"ngram\": \"her medical condition\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I mean when you face death in the eyes, I have so much to look forward to,\\\" Retton said in the interview that aired Monday.\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"death\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"the eyes\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 509}, {\"ngram\": \"Retton\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 553}, {\"ngram\": \"the interview\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: \\\"I am a fighter and I am not going to give up.\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 653, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fighter\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not going to give up.\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have no idea what the future holds for me.\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 725, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 695}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know if I am going to have lasting issues with my lungs.\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lasting issues\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"my lungs\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They do not know.\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 809, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wish I had answers.\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 831, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"answers\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I would never give up.\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 858, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not in me.\\\"\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 875, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sitting with her eldest daughter, Shayla Schrepfer, and breathing with the help of a nasal oxygen tube, Retton said she struggles to discuss ongoing health issues.\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 911, \"end\": 917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shayla\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shayla\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shayla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shayla\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her eldest daughter\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 909}, {\"ngram\": \"the help\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 956}, {\"ngram\": \"a nasal oxygen tube\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"Retton\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"ongoing health issues\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am very private and to come out and talk about it\\\" is difficult, she said.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Usually my interviews are, 'Oh, yes - it felt great to win the Olympics,' you know?\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my interviews\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1142}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is different.\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is serious and this is life and I am so grateful to be here.\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am blessed to be here because there is a time when they were about to put me on life support.\\\"\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1386, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1337}, {\"ngram\": \"life support\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Retton was the first American woman to win an Olympic individual all-around gold when she edged out Romania's Ecaterina Szabo in the 1984 Summer Games in Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1409, \"end\": 1423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Woman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.605475790868624e-15, \"text\": \"American woman\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Woman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Woman\"}, {\"begin\": 1488, \"end\": 1495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\", \"score\": 0.9999216200904375, \"rank\": 7.825489311035076e-05, \"text\": \"Romania\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\"}, {\"begin\": 1498, \"end\": 1513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ecaterina_Szabo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ecaterina Szabo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ecaterina_Szabo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ecaterina_Szabo\"}, {\"begin\": 1542, \"end\": 1553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.05310459285974e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Retton\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic individual all-around gold\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1984 Summer Games\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1538}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That golden moment cemented her fame as one the country's most famous gymnasts.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1635, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That golden moment\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"her fame\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's most famous gymnasts\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was thefirst female athlete depicted on a Wheaties box.\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1682, \"end\": 1690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wheaties\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wheaties\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wheaties\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wheaties\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thefirst female athlete\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2018 \\\"Dancing With the Stars\\\" competitor washospitalized in the intensive care unitand unable to breathe on her own, having contracted a rare form of pneumonia, her family announced in October.\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Stars\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1729}, {\"ngram\": \"the intensive care unitand\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"a rare form\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"pneumonia\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1860}, {\"ngram\": \"her family\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1872}, {\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The public wasn't aware of Retton's condition until daughter McKenna Lane Kelley launched a crowdfunding page.\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 2006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1970, \"end\": 1976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shawn_Kelley\", \"score\": 0.999999999272859, \"rank\": 7.050703080282154e-10, \"text\": \"Kelley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shawn_Kelley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shawn_Kelley\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The public\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1906}, {\"ngram\": \"Retton's condition\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1941}, {\"ngram\": \"a crowdfunding page\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Retton's family sought donations to help cover her hospital bill.\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2073, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Retton's family\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2023}, {\"ngram\": \"donations\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"her hospital bill\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2072}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was not insured at the time of her illness, the family said, leaving fans to wonder how one of America's most famous athletes did not have that protection.\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2105}, {\"ngram\": \"her illness\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"the family\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2132}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2151}, {\"ngram\": \"America's most famous athletes\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2203}, {\"ngram\": \"that protection\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Retton said she was in rough financial shape after her 2018 divorce and the Covid-19 pandemic.\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Retton\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"rough financial shape\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2279}, {\"ngram\": \"her 2018 divorce\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not afford it, I could not afford it, I could not afford it,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2411, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But who would even know that this was going to happen to me?\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2473, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's the bottom line, I could not afford it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2521, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bottom line\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2496}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The family's crowdfunding effort has raised more than $459,000 to date.\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The family's crowdfunding effort\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2555}, {\"ngram\": \"date\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Retton was released from the hospital in late October and returned to her home near Houston.\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2688, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2680, \"end\": 2687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"score\": 0.9999999970227691, \"rank\": 2.9765463760563854e-09, \"text\": \"Houston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Retton\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2602}, {\"ngram\": \"the hospital\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2633}, {\"ngram\": \"late October\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2649}, {\"ngram\": \"her home\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Life goes on, things happen,\\\" said Retton, who now has health insurance.\", \"from\": 2690, \"to\": 2763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Life\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2695}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2711}, {\"ngram\": \"Retton\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2732}, {\"ngram\": \"health insurance\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am all set now.\\\"\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2783, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pneumonia is a lung infection that can be caused by bacteria, viruses or fungi.\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2864, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2785, \"end\": 2794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pneumonia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3359486816961548e-73, \"text\": \"Pneumonia\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pneumonia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pneumonia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lung infection\", \"from\": 2798, \"to\": 2814}, {\"ngram\": \"bacteria\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2845}, {\"ngram\": \"viruses\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2854}, {\"ngram\": \"fungi\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It can cause air sacs in the lungs to fill with fluid or pus, leading to a cough, fever, fatigue and difficulty breathing.\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2987, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"air sacs\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2886}, {\"ngram\": \"the lungs\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 2899}, {\"ngram\": \"fluid\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2918}, {\"ngram\": \"pus\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2925}, {\"ngram\": \"a cough\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 2945}, {\"ngram\": \"fever\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 2952}, {\"ngram\": \"fatigue\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 2961}, {\"ngram\": \"difficulty breathing\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 2986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr. Panagis Galiatsatos, an associate professor of medicine at Johns Hopkins Medicine in Baltimore, said that both viral and bacterial pneumonia \\\"have the same spectrum - from mild cases that can be managed outpatient to severe cases that are leading to respiratory failure.\\\"\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3078, \"end\": 3087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baltimore\", \"score\": 0.999999989835942, \"rank\": 6.8366666865641706e-09, \"text\": \"Baltimore\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baltimore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baltimore\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dr. Panagis Galiatsatos\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3012}, {\"ngram\": \"an associate professor\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3036}, {\"ngram\": \"medicine\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3048}, {\"ngram\": \"Johns Hopkins Medicine\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3074}, {\"ngram\": \"both viral and bacterial pneumonia\", \"from\": 3099, \"to\": 3133}, {\"ngram\": \"the same spectrum\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"mild cases\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3175}, {\"ngram\": \"outpatient\", \"from\": 3196, \"to\": 3206}, {\"ngram\": \"severe cases\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3222}, {\"ngram\": \"respiratory failure\", \"from\": 3243, \"to\": 3262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to theAmerican Lung Association, pneumonia leads to more than a million hospitalizations and more than 50,000 deaths each year in the United States.\", \"from\": 3266, \"to\": 3424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3410, \"end\": 3423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999984156927432, \"rank\": 1.5843266907098532e-05, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theAmerican Lung Association\", \"from\": 3279, \"to\": 3307}, {\"ngram\": \"pneumonia\", \"from\": 3309, \"to\": 3318}, {\"ngram\": \"more than a million hospitalizations\", \"from\": 3328, \"to\": 3364}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 50,000 deaths\", \"from\": 3369, \"to\": 3392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Older adults, young children, people who smoke cigarettes and people with underlying medical conditions such as severe asthma or lung disease are especially vulnerable to infection.\", \"from\": 3425, \"to\": 3606, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Older adults\", \"from\": 3425, \"to\": 3437}, {\"ngram\": \"young children\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3453}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3455, \"to\": 3461}, {\"ngram\": \"cigarettes\", \"from\": 3472, \"to\": 3482}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3493}, {\"ngram\": \"underlying medical conditions\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3528}, {\"ngram\": \"severe asthma or lung disease\", \"from\": 3537, \"to\": 3566}, {\"ngram\": \"infection\", \"from\": 3596, \"to\": 3605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flu viruses, the coronavirus and respiratory syncytial virus (RSV) are all common causes of viral pneumonia.\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3670, \"end\": 3673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Respiratory_syncytial_virus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1052854195074376e-51, \"text\": \"RSV\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Respiratory_syncytial_virus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Respiratory_syncytial_virus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the coronavirus\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3636}, {\"ngram\": \"respiratory syncytial virus\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3668}, {\"ngram\": \"common causes\", \"from\": 3683, \"to\": 3696}, {\"ngram\": \"viral pneumonia\", \"from\": 3700, \"to\": 3715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Common signs include shortness of breath, a high fever and blue lips.\", \"from\": 3717, \"to\": 3786, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Common signs\", \"from\": 3717, \"to\": 3729}, {\"ngram\": \"shortness\", \"from\": 3738, \"to\": 3747}, {\"ngram\": \"breath\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3757}, {\"ngram\": \"a high fever\", \"from\": 3759, \"to\": 3771}, {\"ngram\": \"blue lips\", \"from\": 3776, \"to\": 3785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bacterial pneumonia, meanwhile, is usually caused by one of two types of bacteria.\", \"from\": 3788, \"to\": 3870, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bacterial pneumonia\", \"from\": 3788, \"to\": 3807}, {\"ngram\": \"two types\", \"from\": 3848, \"to\": 3857}, {\"ngram\": \"bacteria\", \"from\": 3861, \"to\": 3869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It tends to be more severe than viral pneumonia and is treated with antibiotics.\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 3951, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"viral pneumonia\", \"from\": 3903, \"to\": 3918}, {\"ngram\": \"antibiotics\", \"from\": 3939, \"to\": 3950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But pneumonia caused by rare bacteria can be more challenging to treat and require longer hospital stays, Galiatsatos said.\", \"from\": 3953, \"to\": 4076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pneumonia\", \"from\": 3957, \"to\": 3966}, {\"ngram\": \"rare bacteria\", \"from\": 3977, \"to\": 3990}, {\"ngram\": \"longer hospital stays\", \"from\": 4036, \"to\": 4057}, {\"ngram\": \"Galiatsatos\", \"from\": 4059, \"to\": 4070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheCenters for Disease Control and Prevention recommendsvaccines for certain groups to protect against pneumococcal disease - a range of bacterial infections that includes pneumonia, as well as sinus and ear infections.\", \"from\": 4078, \"to\": 4297, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"TheCenters\", \"from\": 4078, \"to\": 4088}, {\"ngram\": \"Disease Control\", \"from\": 4093, \"to\": 4108}, {\"ngram\": \"Prevention\", \"from\": 4113, \"to\": 4123}, {\"ngram\": \"certain groups\", \"from\": 4147, \"to\": 4161}, {\"ngram\": \"pneumococcal disease\", \"from\": 4181, \"to\": 4201}, {\"ngram\": \"a range\", \"from\": 4204, \"to\": 4211}, {\"ngram\": \"bacterial infections\", \"from\": 4215, \"to\": 4235}, {\"ngram\": \"pneumonia\", \"from\": 4250, \"to\": 4259}, {\"ngram\": \"sinus and ear infections\", \"from\": 4272, \"to\": 4296}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One such vaccine has been available to older adults and those with high-risk medical conditions since 1984, and two newer shots were approved in the last few years for other age groups.\", \"from\": 4299, \"to\": 4484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One such vaccine\", \"from\": 4299, \"to\": 4315}, {\"ngram\": \"older adults\", \"from\": 4338, \"to\": 4350}, {\"ngram\": \"high-risk medical conditions\", \"from\": 4366, \"to\": 4394}, {\"ngram\": \"two newer shots\", \"from\": 4411, \"to\": 4426}, {\"ngram\": \"the last few years\", \"from\": 4444, \"to\": 4462}, {\"ngram\": \"other age groups\", \"from\": 4467, \"to\": 4483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, pneumococcal vaccines are recommended for all children under age 5 and adults ages 65 and up, as well as anyone with an elevated risk of pneumococcal disease.\", \"from\": 4486, \"to\": 4649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pneumococcal vaccines\", \"from\": 4491, \"to\": 4512}, {\"ngram\": \"all children\", \"from\": 4533, \"to\": 4545}, {\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 4552, \"to\": 4555}, {\"ngram\": \"adults\", \"from\": 4562, \"to\": 4568}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 4596, \"to\": 4602}, {\"ngram\": \"an elevated risk\", \"from\": 4608, \"to\": 4624}, {\"ngram\": \"pneumococcal disease\", \"from\": 4628, \"to\": 4648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, Galiatsatos said, the vaccine is still not considered an \\\"'everyone go out and get it' vaccine.\\\"\", \"from\": 4651, \"to\": 4752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Galiatsatos\", \"from\": 4656, \"to\": 4667}, {\"ngram\": \"the vaccine\", \"from\": 4674, \"to\": 4685}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 4715, \"to\": 4723}, {\"ngram\": \"vaccine\", \"from\": 4743, \"to\": 4750}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We would really recommend these vaccines for the individuals that are most likely to develop streptococcal pneumonia,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4754, \"to\": 4882, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these vaccines\", \"from\": 4781, \"to\": 4795}, {\"ngram\": \"the individuals\", \"from\": 4800, \"to\": 4815}, {\"ngram\": \"streptococcal pneumonia\", \"from\": 4848, \"to\": 4871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Galiatsatos added that pneumonia cases seem particularly high this winter.\", \"from\": 4884, \"to\": 4958, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Galiatsatos\", \"from\": 4884, \"to\": 4895}, {\"ngram\": \"pneumonia cases\", \"from\": 4907, \"to\": 4922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This one can be easily put in the top tier of really bad winters with regards to lung infections such as pneumonia,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4960, \"to\": 5086, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This one\", \"from\": 4961, \"to\": 4969}, {\"ngram\": \"the top tier\", \"from\": 4991, \"to\": 5003}, {\"ngram\": \"really bad winters\", \"from\": 5007, \"to\": 5025}, {\"ngram\": \"regards\", \"from\": 5031, \"to\": 5038}, {\"ngram\": \"lung infections\", \"from\": 5042, \"to\": 5057}, {\"ngram\": \"pneumonia\", \"from\": 5066, \"to\": 5075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thus far, neither Retton nor her family has disclosed details about which type of pneumonia she contracted, the particular treatments she received or her vaccination status.\", \"from\": 5088, \"to\": 5261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"neither Retton\", \"from\": 5098, \"to\": 5112}, {\"ngram\": \"her family\", \"from\": 5117, \"to\": 5127}, {\"ngram\": \"details\", \"from\": 5142, \"to\": 5149}, {\"ngram\": \"which type\", \"from\": 5156, \"to\": 5166}, {\"ngram\": \"pneumonia\", \"from\": 5170, \"to\": 5179}, {\"ngram\": \"the particular treatments\", \"from\": 5196, \"to\": 5221}, {\"ngram\": \"her vaccination status\", \"from\": 5238, \"to\": 5260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, she said her bout with pneumonia could have killed her if not for a neighbor who noticed that her car door was left open in the driveway.\", \"from\": 5263, \"to\": 5409, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bout\", \"from\": 5285, \"to\": 5289}, {\"ngram\": \"pneumonia\", \"from\": 5295, \"to\": 5304}, {\"ngram\": \"a neighbor\", \"from\": 5338, \"to\": 5348}, {\"ngram\": \"her car door\", \"from\": 5366, \"to\": 5378}, {\"ngram\": \"the driveway\", \"from\": 5396, \"to\": 5408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The former gymnast was on her bedroom floor unable to move when that neighbor, concerned about that open car door, let herself in to check on Retton.\", \"from\": 5411, \"to\": 5560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The former gymnast\", \"from\": 5411, \"to\": 5429}, {\"ngram\": \"her bedroom floor\", \"from\": 5437, \"to\": 5454}, {\"ngram\": \"that neighbor\", \"from\": 5475, \"to\": 5488}, {\"ngram\": \"that open car door\", \"from\": 5506, \"to\": 5524}, {\"ngram\": \"Retton\", \"from\": 5553, \"to\": 5559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She came in the house, she knows my code, and saw me and found me and pretty much saved my life,\\\" Retton said.\", \"from\": 5562, \"to\": 5673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the house\", \"from\": 5575, \"to\": 5584}, {\"ngram\": \"my code\", \"from\": 5596, \"to\": 5603}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 5651, \"to\": 5658}, {\"ngram\": \"Retton\", \"from\": 5661, \"to\": 5667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aria Bendix is the breaking health reporter for NBC News Digital.\", \"from\": 5675, \"to\": 5740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5675, \"end\": 5679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aria_Montgomery\", \"score\": 0.9999996880338162, \"rank\": 3.0744247687393915e-07, \"text\": \"Aria\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aria_Montgomery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aria_Montgomery\"}, {\"begin\": 5680, \"end\": 5686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bendix_Corporation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.732298100374186e-20, \"text\": \"Bendix\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bendix_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bendix_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 5723, \"end\": 5739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCNews.com\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC News Digital\", \"types